data.description: Discover charm and comfort in this inviting 3-bedroom/2-bath ranch-style home nestled in Charlotte. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating a perfect space for gatherings and family moments. The heart of the home, the updated kitchen with contemporary appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a joy. Three bedrooms provide comfortable space each filled with natural light. Outside, a private backyard beckons, offering a peaceful retreat for outdoor activities and relaxation. Imagine summer barbecues, lazy afternoons, and vibrant sunsets enjoyed in the comfort of your own space. Solar panels.Located in vibrant Charlotte, this home is ideally situated for those seeking both a tranquil residential setting and easy access to the city's amenities.From cultural attractions to dining and shopping, you'll find everything you need just a short drive away. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming residence your home sweet home.
